rows.label: bf08090100_0010
rows.name:
W-what...
What did you do to me?

rows.label: bf08090100_0020
rows.name: Easy. You'll be fine.

rows.label: bf08090100_0030
rows.name: It's not perfect. So don't come complaining to me.

rows.label: bf08090100_0040
rows.name: Hikari...

rows.label: bf08090100_0050
rows.name: My name... You still remember it, do you?

rows.label: bf08090100_0060
rows.name:
I guess that makes sense.
You never did return to your crystal, did you?

rows.label: bf08090100_0070
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08090100_0080
rows.name: Better thank your good luck.

rows.label: bf08090100_0090
rows.name:
You've been given the second chance you
denied to many brave Superbians.

rows.label: bf08090100_0100
rows.name:
I doubt your luck would hold up so well if Meleph
were here!

rows.label: bf08090100_0110
rows.name: Hikari... Didn't you and Shin...?

rows.label: bf08090100_0120
rows.name:
Yes.
We fought together against Metsu, once.

rows.label: bf08090100_0130
rows.name: That's why I need to know...

rows.label: bf08090100_0140
rows.name:
Why?
Why did you take Metsu's side?

rows.label: bf08090100_0150
rows.name: What's the point?

rows.label: bf08090100_0160
rows.name: Knowing will only make you despair in humans too.

rows.label: bf08090100_0170
rows.name: I can guess.

rows.label: bf08090100_0180
rows.name:
And I can tell you...
It didn't lead me to the same conclusion as you.

rows.label: bf08090100_0190
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08090100_0200
rows.name:
Laura...
She's in there, isn't she?

rows.label: bf08090100_0210
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf08090100_0220
rows.name:
With everything you've done,
we can't forgive you.

rows.label: bf08090100_0230
rows.name: And if you're going to keep standing in our way in the future,

rows.label: bf08090100_0235
rows.name: keep trying to destroy the world, we will stop you.

rows.label: bf08090100_0240
rows.name: But, right now...

rows.label: bf08090100_0250
rows.name: Wise decision.

rows.label: bf08090100_0260
rows.name:
This is the Land of Mors.
A demon world beyond our imagination.

rows.label: bf08090100_0270
rows.name: You know it?

rows.label: bf08090100_0280
rows.name: This land was destroyed long before Alst existed.

rows.label: bf08090100_0290
rows.name: The birthplace of God.

rows.label: bf08090100_0300
rows.name: That's what Metsu said.

rows.label: bf08090100_0310
rows.name: This is...God's...

rows.label: bf08090100_0320
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: bf08090100_0330
rows.name:
I know full well there's no easy
way to change your mind.

rows.label: bf08090100_0340
rows.name: But hear me out.

rows.label: bf08090100_0350
rows.name: Let's regroup, and climb up the World Tree.

rows.label: bf08090100_0360
rows.name: Call it a ceasefire until then, OK?

rows.label: bf08090100_0370
rows.name: A united front?

rows.label: bf08090100_0375
rows.name: As you wish...

rows.label: bf08090100_0380
rows.name:
...It's not like I could take you on
in this state anyway.
